org.ogcs.netty.impl

类 TcpProtocolClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ogcs.netty.impl.TcpProtocolClient
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    NettyBootstrap<io.netty.bootstrap.Bootstrap>

    public abstract class TcpProtocolClient
extends java.lang.Object
implements NettyBootstrap<io.netty.bootstrap.Bootstrap>
    TcpProtocolClient make easy to create tcp client. The start() method use to tcp client connect to remote address. The stop() method use to the client disconnect.
    从以下版本开始:
    1.0
